issue.title: Error of Loading Husky in My Own World File.

content.raw:
Hi Nathan,

Thanks for your reply. I am shamed for my spelling mistakes in the
question, but I did spell right in my SDF, and I think I did not make
myself clear.

Actually I loaded the robot into my world successfully, but the warning
drove my attention to libhusky_gazebo_plugins.so  which is wrote in the
code of husky.

Since I am going to write a control plugin of my robot model, I am curious
about  libhusky_gazebo_plugins.so and its function. Because I have not seen
another plugin used in SDF (instead of URDF), I really want to get access
to the source code of this plugin (libhusky_gazebo_plugins.so). Do you have
any ideas of it?

Thanks for your time.

Yajing
